```c
void ECRYPT_keystream_bytes(ECRYPT_ctx *x,u8 *stream,u32 bytes)
{
  u32 i;
  for (i = 0;i < bytes;++i) stream[i] = 0;
  ECRYPT_encrypt_bytes(x,stream,stream,bytes);
}
```

ie setting `Output(c, bytes)` to call `Crypt(c, c, bytes)`?

